## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fecb-129">Если соответствующий результат не найден, <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesCOMException> возникает исключение с кодом ошибки 0x2030.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fecb-129">If no matching result is found, a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesCOMException> with error code 0x2030 is thrown.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fecb-130">Следующий пример Visual Basic .NET создает новый <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> объект с указанным путем, затем создает новую запись в контейнере и сохраняет ее.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fecb-130">The following Visual Basic .NET example creates a new <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> object with the specified path, then creates a new entry in the container and saves it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fecb-131">Он пытается получить только что созданную запись.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fecb-131">It attempts to retrieve the newly created entry.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Try  
     Dim myEntry1 As DirectoryEntry  
     Dim myEntry2 As DirectoryEntry  
     Dim strPath As String = "LDAP://DC=fabrikam,DC=com"  
  
     ' Create a 'DirectoryEntry' object with the given path.  
     Dim myDE As New DirectoryEntry(strPath)  
     Dim myEntries As DirectoryEntries = myDE.Children  
  
     ' Create a new entry in the container.  
     myEntry1 = myEntries.Add("CN=Sample Entry", myDE.SchemaClassName)  
     ' Save changes in the 'Active Directory Domain Services' store.  
     myEntry1.CommitChanges()  
  
     ' Find a child in the 'DirectoryEntries' collection which has the   
     ' specified name and type.  
     myEntry2 = myEntries.Find("CN=Sample Entry", myDE.SchemaClassName)  
     Console.WriteLine(myEntry2.Name + " is found in container.")  
  
     Catch e As Exception  
          Console.WriteLine("The following exception was raised : {0}", e.Message.ToString())  
     End Try  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fecb-132">В следующем C# примере показано, как создать новый <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> объект с указанным путем, затем создать новую запись в контейнере и сохранить ее.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fecb-132">The following C# example shows how to create a new <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> object with the specified path, then creates a new entry in the container and saves it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fecb-133">Он пытается получить только что созданную запись.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fecb-133">It attempts to retrieve the newly- created entry.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.DirectoryServices;   
  
class MyClass1  
{  
   static void Main()  
   {  
      try  
      {          
         DirectoryEntry myEntry1;  
         DirectoryEntry myEntry2;  
         String strPath = "LDAP://DC=fabrikam,DC=com";  
  
         // Create a 'DirectoryEntry' object with the given path.  
         DirectoryEntry myDE = new DirectoryEntry(strPath);  
         DirectoryEntries myEntries = myDE.Children;  
  
         // Create a new entry in the container.  
         myEntry1 = myEntries.Add("CN=Sample Entry",myDE.SchemaClassName);  
         // Save changes in the 'Active Directory Domain Services' store.  
         myEntry1.CommitChanges();  
  
         // Find a child in the 'DirectoryEntries' collection which has the   
         // specified name and type.  
         myEntry2 = myEntries.Find("CN=Sample Entry",myDE.SchemaClassName);  
         Console.WriteLine (myEntry2.Name + " is found in container.");  
  
      }  
      catch(Exception e)  
      {  
         Console.WriteLine("The following exception was raised : {0}",e.Message);  
      }  
   }  
}  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2fecb-134">В следующем C++ примере создается новый <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> объект с указанным путем, затем создается новая запись в контейнере и сохраняется.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fecb-134">The following C++ example creates a new <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> object with the specified path, then creates a new entry in the container and saves it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fecb-135">Он пытается получить новую запись.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fecb-135">It attempts to retrieve the new entry.</span></span>  
  
